OL,3,CThe reality of having a loved one with
OL,4,Cdementia - and fears for Wales' future
OL,6,FAnticipating the next phone call,
OL,7,Flosing the loved one you once knew and
OL,8,Fdreading the day they could forget who
OL,9,Fyou are.
OL,11,FThat's the reality for family members
OL,12,Fwhose loved ones live with dementia.
OL,14,FGloria Cavanagh, 79, is one of at
OL,15,Fleast 42,000 people in Wales living
OL,16,Fwith the condition. Her daughter
OL,17,FNatalie shared her experience of the
OL,18,F"cruel" disease on ITV Wales' Sharp
OL,19,FEnd programme.
