OL,3,CThe reality of having a loved one with
OL,4,Cdementia - and fears for Wales' future
OL,6,F"She was down the bank every day
OL,7,Fbecause she'd lost her cards. She was
OL,8,Falways asking people to help her do
OL,9,Fthings, but she just went down and
OL,10,Fdown. Then when she was on medication,
OL,11,Fshe took too much and ended up in
OL,12,Fhospital because she'd forgot that
OL,13,Fshe'd taken it. And then we just went
OL,14,Fon a downhill slope from that."
