OL,3,CThe reality of having a loved one with
OL,4,Cdementia - and fears for Wales' future
OL,6,FGloria's admission led to her
OL,7,Fdiagnosis of dementia and after the
OL,8,Fhospital stay she was placed in
OL,9,Fsheltered accommodation.
OL,11,F"It was tough as a family," Natalie
OL,12,Fsays. "All she did in there was stay
OL,13,Fin bed all day - from the time she
OL,14,Fwoke up in the morning, until the time
OL,15,Fthe carers left after giving her
OL,16,Fmedication.
