OL,3,CThe reality of having a loved one with
OL,4,Cdementia - and fears for Wales' future
OL,6,FNatalie is not alone - the need for
OL,7,Funpaid care, often provided by loved
OL,8,Fones or friends, will grow
OL,9,Fsignificantly by 2040 with 43% more
OL,10,Fpeople expected to require unpaid
OL,11,Fcare. It's estimated that nearly
OL,12,F70,000 people in Wales will be living
OL,13,Fwith dementia by 2040.
OL,15,FThankfully, Gloria received respite
OL,16,Fcare at a council-run home locally in
OL,17,FPenarth while Natalie needed to take
OL,18,Ftime away.
