OL,3,CThe reality of having a loved one with
OL,4,Cdementia - and fears for Wales' future
OL,6,FThe cost of dementia care in Wales has
OL,7,Fnow reached #2 billion per year. This
OL,8,Ffigure is set to rise to more than
OL,9,F#4.5 billion by 2040 unless urgent
OL,10,Faction is taken, according to the
OL,11,FAlzheimer's Society.
OL,13,FAnd there's high demand for places in
OL,14,Fcare homes, which face many of their
OL,15,Fown challenges.
OL,17,FClare O'Toole is the manager at Ty
OL,18,FDewi Sant Residential Home, where
OL,19,FGloria is now a permanent resident.
OL,20,FShe says there are always more
OL,21,Fresidents on a waiting list to get in.
