OL,3,CThe reality of having a loved one with
OL,4,Cdementia - and fears for Wales' future
OL,6,FShe said: "I've been here in this
OL,7,Fparticular home for nine years. And
OL,8,Fsince I've been here, we've actually
OL,9,Fintroduced our own dementia unit
OL,10,Fbecause demand was so high."
OL,12,FDespite this high demand, recruiting
OL,13,Fcare staff is difficult: "We
OL,14,Fconstantly have vacancies. That's not
OL,15,Fjust in our home, that's in our sister
OL,16,Fhomes as well.
