OL,3,CThe reality of having a loved one with
OL,4,Cdementia - and fears for Wales' future
OL,6,F"(Carers) get the real living wage,
OL,7,Fbut it's still the same price that
OL,8,Fthey would get, for example, in Tescos
OL,9,F- and it's a far harder job and a lot
OL,10,Fof responsibility that goes into
OL,11,Fcaring for an individual.
OL,13,F"It needs to be promoted - how
OL,14,Fenjoyable it is to actually work in
OL,15,Fcare, because I do not think that Joe
OL,16,FBloggs in the street understands how
OL,17,Fmuch joy you can get out of this job.
