OL,3,CThe reality of having a loved one with
OL,4,Cdementia - and fears for Wales' future
OL,6,F"It's not all negative, it's very
OL,7,Fenjoyable. When you leave here at the
OL,8,Fend of the day, you feel like you've
OL,9,Fmade a difference to somebody's life
OL,10,Fand that is invaluable.
OL,12,FClare hopes the Welsh Government will
OL,13,Fprioritise recruitment of carers. She
OL,14,Fadded: "I feel appreciated from within
OL,15,Four care home sector, within the
OL,16,Fcouncil I feel very appreciated - but
OL,17,Fas far as outside of that, I would say
OL,18,Fnot really."
