OL,3,CThe reality of having a loved one with
OL,4,Cdementia - and fears for Wales' future
OL,6,FDoes a care home manager like Clare
OL,7,Fworry about the future? "I do because
OL,8,FI don't feel that enough is being done
OL,9,Fin regards to having the facilities
OL,10,Ffor our ageing generation," she says.
OL,12,F"Dementia intake has gone up high and
OL,13,Fthere's not the placement for them.
OL,14,FWhen they're at home they've got their
OL,15,Frelative caring for them and it's a 24
OL,16,Fhour, seven days a week job that comes
OL,17,Fwith a lot of stress.
