OL,3,CThe reality of having a loved one with
OL,4,Cdementia - and fears for Wales' future
OL,6,F"By the time they come to us, they
OL,7,Fjust haven't got any more to give. And
OL,8,Fit's affecting that person's health as
OL,9,Fwell, which also has effects on our
OL,10,FNHS and our health service. So they
OL,11,Fneed to really be creating a lot more
OL,12,Fhomes to be able to meet capacity."
