OL,3,CThe reality of having a loved one with
OL,4,Cdementia - and fears for Wales' future
OL,6,FCllr Lis Burnett, Leader of the Vale
OL,7,Fof Glamorgan Council, said: "The
OL,8,Fincredible challenges councils face in
OL,9,Ffunding public services are now very
OL,10,Fwell documented. One of the biggest
OL,11,Fpressures on our budget is the ageing
OL,12,Fpopulation of the Vale and the growing
OL,13,Fnumber of adults needing social care.
OL,14,FWe are also seeing a steady increase
OL,15,Fin the complexity of the care they
OL,16,Fneed. Around thirty one per-cent of
OL,17,Fall Council spending this year will be
OL,18,Fon delivering social care. This will
OL,19,Fbe around #96m.
