OL,3,CThe reality of having a loved one with
OL,4,Cdementia - and fears for Wales' future
OL,6,F"The current situation, however, is
OL,7,Fjust not sustainable. Our Council is
OL,8,Fprioritising funding services such as
OL,9,Fsocial care and additional learning
OL,10,Fneeds provision in education. We are
OL,11,Fputting first the needs of those who
OL,12,Fneed us the most. To continue to be
OL,13,Fable to do this we are rapidly having
OL,14,Fto change the way in which we deliver
OL,15,Fother services that are provided to
OL,16,Fall residents."
