OL,3,CThe reality of having a loved one with
OL,4,Cdementia - and fears for Wales' future
OL,6,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Our Dementia Action Plan sets out our
OL,8,Fvision for Wales to be a dementia-
OL,9,Ffriendly nation that recognises the
OL,10,Frights of people with dementia to feel
OL,11,Fvalued and to live as independently as
OL,12,Fpossible.
OL,14,F"With dementia rates set to rise, we
OL,15,Fwill consider the impact on
OL,16,Fcommunities as we develop the next
OL,17,Fsteps for our Dementia Action Plan."
